        <description>Comma operator for 循环使用 ; 分隔的三个 control expression 控制循环过程. 1 2 3 4 for (initialization; test; update) statement /* can be a simple statement or a compound statement */ for (n = 0; n &amp;lt; 10; n++) printf(&amp;#34;%d %d\n&amp;#34;, n, 2 * n + 1) /* &amp;#34;,&amp;#34; here is not comma operator, but separator, see below */</description>
        
